\c 6
\s Jesu Ishe wesabata
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakaitika nesabata rechipiri shure kwerekutanga, kuti paakanga achifamba napakati peminda yezviyo, vadzidzi vake vakatanha hura dzezviyo, vakadya, vachidzipukuta namavoko
\v 2 Zvino vamwe vavaFarisi vakati kwavari: Munoitireiko zvisina kutenderwa kuitwa nemisi yesabata?
\v 3 Jesu achivapindura, akati: Ko hamuna kurava pamusoro pezvizvi here? zvakaitwa naDhavhidhi, musi waakanga ava nenzara iye navakanga vanaye,
\v 4 kuti wakapinda sei mumba maMwari, akatora, akadya, zvingwa zvokuratidza, akapavo vakanga vanaye; izvo zvakanga zvisina kutenderwa kudyiwa, asi navaprista voga?
\v 5 Akati kwavari: Mwanakomana womunhu ndiyevo Ishe wesabata.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu waiva neruvoko rwakawonyana
\p
\v 6 Zvino kwakaitikavo nerimwe sabata kuti wakapinda musinagoge, akadzidzisa; zvino kwakanga kunomunhu ipapo aneruvoko rwake rworudyi rwakawonyana.
\v 7 Vanyori navaFarisi vakamutarisisa, \add kuvona\add* kana angaporesa nomusi wesabata, kuti vawane kumupomera mhosva
\v 8 Asi iye wakaziva mifungo yavo, akati kumunhu wakanga anoruvoko rwakawonyana: Simuka, umire pakati \add pavanhu\add*. Akasimuka akamira.
\v 9 Zvino Jesu akati kwavari: Ndinokubvunzai chinhu chimwe: Zvinotenderwa here kuita zvakanaka kana zvakaipa nesabata? kuponesa upenyu kana kuparadza?
\v 10 Ipapo akaringa-ringa kwavari vose, akati kumurume: Tambanudza ruvoko rwako. Akaita saizvozvo. ruvoko rwake rukaporeswa rukava sorumwe.
\v 11 Vakazara noupengo, vakarangana mumwe nomumwe kuti Jesu vangamuitei.
\s Jesu unodana vadzidzi vake
\p
\v 12 Zvino kwakaitika namazuva iwayo kuti wakabuda akaenda kugomo kundonyengetera, akapedza vusiku hwose mukunyengetera kuna Mwari.
\v 13 Zvino kwakati kwaedza, akadana vadzidzi vake; akasanangura kwavari vanegumi navaviri vaakatumidzavo kuti vapositora;
\v 14 Simoni, waakatumidzavo Petro, naAndiriya, munun'una wake, naJakobho, naJohwani, naFiripi, naBartoromeo,
\v 15 Matewu naTomasi, Jakobho waArifiyosi, naSimoni wainzi Ziroti;
\v 16 naJudhasi waJakobho, naJudhasi Isikariyoti, wakazova mutengesi.
\v 17 Akaburuka navo, akamira pakaenzana navadzidzi vake vazhinji, nechaunga chikuru chavanhu, vaibva Judhiya rose neJerusarema, napamahombekombe egungwa reTire neSidoni. vakavuya kuzomunzwa, nokuporeswa hosha dzavo;
\v 18 navakanga vachitambudziwa nemweya yetsvina, vakaporeswa.
\v 19 Chaunga chose chikatsvaka kumunyangata: nokuti kwakabuda simba kwaari rikaporesa vose.
\s Mharidzo yaJesu
\p
\v 20 Zvino wakasimudzira meso ake kuvadzidzi vake, akati: Makaropafadzwa varombo, nokuti vushe bwaMwari ndobwenyu.
\v 21 Makaropafadzwa munenzara zvino, nokuti muchagutiswa. Makaropafadzwa munochema zvino, nokuti muchaseka.
\v 22 Makaropafadzwa imwi, kana vanhu vachikuvengai, vachikudzingai, vachikunyombai, vachirasha zita renyu serakashata, nokuda koMwanakomana womunhu.
\v 23 Farai nezuva iro, mupembere nomufaro, nokuti tarirai, mubairo wenyu mukuru kudenga ; nokuti saizvozvo \add ndizvo\add* zvakaita madzibaba avo kuvaporofita.
\v 24 Asi munenhamo imwi vafumi! Nokuti mapiwa nyaradzo yenyu.
\v 25 Munenhamo imwi makaguta! Nokuti muchava nenzara. Munenhamo imwi munoseka zvino! Nokuti muchachema nokuwungudza.
\v 26 Munenhamo imwi kana vanhu vose vachitaura zvakanaka pamusoro penyu! Nokuti ndizvo zvakaita madzibaba avo kuvaporofita venhema.
\v 27 Asi ndinoti kwamuri imwi munonzwa: Idai vavengi venyu, itai zvakanaka kune avo vanokuvengai,
\v 28 Muropafadze avo vanokutukai, munyengeterere avo vanokukubatai zvakaipa.
\v 29 Kune uyo unokurova padama, umupe rimwevo; unokutorera nguvo yokunze, usarambidza nenguvo yomukativo.
\v 30 Upe umwe noumwe unokumbira kwauri; nounokutorera zvako, usazvikumbirazve.
\v 31 Sezvamunoda kuti vanhu vakuitirei, muvaitirevo saizvozvo.
\v 32 Kana muchida avo vanokudai, munokuvongwa kwakadiniko? Nokuti navatadzivo vanoda vanovada.
\v 33 Kana muchiitira zvakanaka kune avo vanokuitirai zvakanaka, munokuvongwa kwakadiniko? Nokuti navatadzi vanoitavo saizvozvo.
\v 34 Kana muchikwereta vamunotarisira kudzoserwa navo, munokuvongwa kwakadiniko? Nokuti navatadzi vanokweretesavo vatadzi, kuti vapiwezve zvakaenzana nazvo.
\v 35 Asi idai vavengi venyu, muite zvakanaka, mupe chikwereti musingatarisirizve chinhu; zvino mubairo wenyu uchava mukuru, mugova vana voWokumusoro-soro; nokuti iye unomoyo munyoro kunavasingavongi navakaipa.
\v 36 Naizvozvo ivai netsitsi, sababa venyuvo vanetsitsi.
\v 37 Musatonga, nemwi hamungazotongwi; musapa mhaka, nemwi hamungazopiwi mhaka; regererai, nemwi mucharegererwa.
\v 38 Ipai, nemwi muchapiwa; chiyero chakanaka, chakatsikirirwa, chakazunguzirwa, chinopfachukira; vachakupai pachifuva chenyu. Nokuti nechiyero chamunoyera nacho, muchayererwavo nacho.
\v 39 Akataura mufananidzo kwavari, \add akati\add*: Bofu ringatungamirira bofu here? Haangawiri mugomba ose here?
\v 40 Mudzidzi haapfuvuri mudzidzisi wake; asi mumwe nomumwe, kana akwaniswa, uchava somudzidzisi wake.
\v 41 Vuye unotarireiko rubanzu ruri muziso reumwe wako, asi puranga riri muziso rako haurivoni?
\v 42 Kana ungareva seiko kuneumwe wako, \add uchiti\add*: Umwe wangu, rega ndibudise rubanzu ruri muziso rako, iwe pachako usingavoni puranga riri muziso rako? Iwe munyengeri, tanga ubvise puranga muziso rako, ipapo uchavonesesa kubvisa rubanzu ruri muziso rehama yako.
\v 43 Nokuti hakunomuti wakanaka unobereka zvibereko zvakaipa; vuye muti wakaipa unobereka zvibereko zvakanaka.
\v 44 nokuti muti umwe nomumwe unozikamwa nezvibereko zvawo. Nokuti vanhu havatanhi mavonde pamhinzwa, kana mazambiringa haatamwi parukato.
\v 45 Munhu wakanaka kubva pafuma yomoyo, wake yakanaka, Unobudisa zvakanaka munhu wakaipa kubva pafuma yomoyo wake yakaipa unobudisa zvakaipa; nokuti muromo wake unotaura kubva pakuzara komoyo wake.
\s Mufananidzo weimba yakavakwa paruware
\p
\v 46 Munondiidzireiko Ishe! Ishe! Musingaiti zvandinoreva?
\v 47 Ani nani unovuya kwandiri, akanzwa mashoko angu akaaita, ndichakuratidzai waakafanana naye.
\v 48 Wakafanana nomunhu wakavaka imba, akachera, akadzikisa, akateya nheyo paruware; mvura zhinji ikavuya, rukova rwukarova imba iyo nesimba, ikasagona kuizunungusa, nokuti yakanga yakateyiwa paruware.
\v 49 Asi unonzwa, asingaiti, wakafanana nomunhu wakavaka imba isinenheyo pavhu; mvura yakati ichiirova nesimba, ikawa pakarepo, kuputsika kweimba iyo kukava kukuru.
